{"items":[{"id":"22689","user":{"id":"179794","nickname":"ftxqgfudi","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/community_frontend/community_default_avatar/avatar_300x300_01.jpg","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>这个问题我知道，只是没打而已。</p>\n<p>毕竟治标不治本，还是不能进行数据类型的转换。</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1495613616,"created_at":1495613616,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"22687","user":{"id":"197032","nickname":"猫老祖","avatar_url":"https://static-platform.codemao.cn/production/avatar/custom/31598a68-64e3-4c62-9843-9438a63162e5","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>唔，这个嘛... &nbsp;我们可以用一个中间变量来解决这个问题。</p>\n<p>首先把字符串中需要取变量的部分设为变量N，这样就可以放在运算积木中计算了。</p>\n<p>对了还要提醒的是，字符串\"1abc\"中，第1到第2个字符取出来是：\"1a\"，这样依然是个字符串，计算会出错。所以如果要取出变量：1，积木需要这样写：第1到第1个字符。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fk9EoG4TcCwRqy2kWPDgN-Flnj5J\"><br></p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1495607908,"created_at":1495607908,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"22368","user":{"id":"179794","nickname":"ftxqgfudi","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/community_frontend/community_default_avatar/avatar_300x300_01.jpg","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>猫老祖说不能进行数据类型的转换<img src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/af/cry.gif\"></p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1495347315,"created_at":1495347315,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"22363","user":{"id":"179794","nickname":"ftxqgfudi","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/community_frontend/community_default_avatar/avatar_300x300_01.jpg","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>对</p>\n<p>但是我的变量是一个数字，但是这样一取第一到第二个字符就变成了字符串，怎么能够把字符串变成数字呢？</p>\n<p>就像是python中的int(\"123\")</p>\n<p>还有，怎么把数字转成字符串？就像str(123)</p>\n<p>求解，这个钟表不好做啊</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1495346800,"created_at":1495346800,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"22362","user":{"id":"204645","nickname":"小假LittleFalse","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fqw3NfVBhmglR3dOjGtkKh5J2oXD","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>字符属于文本类</p>\n<p>0那个地方属于数值类型</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1495346677,"created_at":1495346677,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"22360","user":{"id":"179794","nickname":"ftxqgfudi","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/community_frontend/community_default_avatar/avatar_300x300_01.jpg","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FoshRGJpnWQmxSj-d7XwW0WK8PGD\"><br></p>\n<p>附图。</p>\n<p>就是下面的模块拼不到0那个地方。</p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1495346617,"created_at":1495346617,"earliest_comments":[]}],"offset":0,"limit":30,"total":6,"counted":true}